=== 評價 ===
《寶可夢 黑／白》獲得許多好評，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的總分是87%，其中包括許多讚賞<ref name="MC">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/ds/pokemon-black-version/critic-reviews |title=Pokemon Black Version Critic Reviews for DS at Metacritic.com |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2011-06-09 |archive-date=2012-01-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64uhmQJju?url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/ds/pokemon-black-version/critic-reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。日本雜誌《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》給了遊戲40/40的滿分，這是第十五個獲得滿分的遊戲、也是該雜誌給寶可夢系列電子遊戲的最高分<ref name="escapist">{{cite web |title=Pokemon Black & White Grab Rare Perfect Score from Famitsu |publisher=''The Escapist'' |last=Funk |first=John |date=2010-09-08 |accessdate=2010-09-08 |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/103311-Pokemon-Black-White-Grab-Rare-Perfect-Score-from-Famitsu |archive-date=2019-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723131546/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/103311-Pokemon-Black-White-Grab-Rare-Perfect-Score-from-Famitsu |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]的Annette Gonzalez撰文評論、表示《寶可夢 黑／白》是建立在紮實基礎上的傑作，並將整個系列作提升至新的水準<ref name="GI">{{cite journal|journal=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|issue=215|date=March 2011|page=95|last=Gonzalez|first=Annette}}</ref>。[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]的評論家Jamin Smith則認為遊戲的創新程度不如預期，但仍表示「《寶可夢 黑／白》是個超讚的傑作、而且是系列裡最好的遊戲。」<ref name="VG">{{cite web |url=http://www.videogamer.com/ds/pokemon_black/review.html |title=Pokemon Black Version Review for DS - VideoGamer.com |publisher=[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]] |first=Jamin |last=Smith |date=2011-02-14 |accessdate=2011-02-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717202218/http://www.videogamer.com/ds/pokemon_black/review.html |archivedate=2011-07-17 |df= }}</ref>《[[官方任天堂雜誌|官方任天堂雜誌]]》將這個作品譽為「美妙精緻的傑作」<ref name="ONM">{{cite journal|journal=Official Nintendo Magazine|date=Mar 2011 |page=87}}</ref>。《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》則表示「寶可夢系列的新作一如既往地令人上癮」<ref name="NP">{{cite journal|title=''[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]]''|publisher=Future Publishing |date=March 2011 |page=82}}</ref>。<!--''[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]'' acknowledged that "where next for ''Pokémon'' ''Black'' and ''White'' don't suggest any answers, but they do remind us why we'd care in the first place."--><ref name="Edge">{{cite journal|journal=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]|date=March 2011 |page=103}}</ref>

[[IGN|IGN]]給了遊戲9/10的高分，比其它[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]的寶可夢遊戲都還要高。並解釋：「有一些新寶可夢的美術設計實在該被批評，不過整體而言仍是很棒的遊戲，它激起了我對怪物戰鬥的渴望和興趣」<ref name="IGN Review">{{cite web|title=Pokemon Black Review|publisher=IGN|last=DeVries|first=Jack|date=2011-03-04|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/115/1153589p1.html|archive-date=2013-07-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IKdU1BT5?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/03/05/pokemon-white-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Retronauts的Jeremy Parish則批評：「才開始沒多久就讓我厭煩了，和以前的《寶可夢》如出一轍。」<ref>{{cite web|title=A Super-Effective Pokemon Talk|url=http://podcast.the1upnetwork.com/flat/Retronauts/R030611.mp3|publisher=1UP.com|accessdate=2011-03-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64uht6sOf?url=http://podcast.the1upnetwork.com/flat/Retronauts/R030611.mp3|archivedate=2012-01-23}}</ref>[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的編輯Carolyn Gudmundson評論：「雖然它仍擺脫不了系列一貫的模式，但《黑／白》還是有足夠的新內容、深奧的戰鬥學問能讓你永無止盡地玩下去。如果你只能選一款遊戲與你共度餘生，《黑／白》是明智的抉擇。」<ref name="Gradar">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/ds/pokemon-black-white/review/pokemon-black-and-white-review/a-2011030319838142019/g-201004091000657031 |title=Pokemon Black and White review, Pokemon Black / White Review, DS Reviews |publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |first=Carolyn |last=Gudmundson |date=2011-03-04 |accessdate=2011-04-06 |archive-date=2012-01-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64uiHfBX6?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/pokemon-black-and-white-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

